# React to Inertia.js with Vue 3 Conversion Guide

## Overview

This guide covers converting a React SPA to a **Laravel + Inertia.js + Vue 3** stack. Vue 3 uses Single File Components (SFCs) with the Composition API (preferred) and `<script setup>` syntax. The Laravel side is identical to the React adapter — only the frontend view layer changes.

## Tech Stack

- **Laravel**: 12.x
- **Inertia.js**: 2.x (`inertiajs/inertia-laravel`)
- **Inertia Vue adapter**: `@inertiajs/vue3` 2.x
- **Vue**: 3.x (Composition API + `<script setup>`)
- **Tailwind CSS**: 4.x
- **Vite**: 6.x

