## Event Handling

| React JSX | Vue Template |
|-----------|-------------|
| `onClick={fn}` | `@click="fn"` |
| `onClick={() => fn(id)}` | `@click="fn(id)"` |
| `onClick={e => e.stopPropagation()}` | `@click.stop="fn"` |
| `onChange={e => setVal(e.target.value)}` | `v-model="val"` |
| `onSubmit={handleSubmit}` | `@submit.prevent="handleSubmit"` |
| `onKeyDown={e => ...}` | `@keydown="fn"` |

### Controlled vs v-model

**React:**

```jsx
<input value={name} onChange={e => setName(e.target.value)} />
```

**Vue:**

```vue
<input v-model="name" />
<!-- v-model is shorthand for :value="name" @input="name = $event.target.value" -->
```

