## Layouts

### Persistent Layout in Vue

```vue
<!-- resources/js/Layouts/AppLayout.vue -->
<template>
    <div>
        <nav><!-- Navbar --></nav>
        <main>
            <!-- slot = children in React terms -->
            <slot />
        </main>
    </div>
</template>
```

```vue
<!-- resources/js/Pages/Home.vue -->
<script setup>
import AppLayout from '@/Layouts/AppLayout.vue';

// Attach persistent layout (Navbar won't remount on navigation)
defineOptions({
    layout: AppLayout,
});
</script>

<template>
    <div>Home content</div>
</template>
```

