## Common Patterns

### Conditional Rendering

**React:**

```jsx
{isLoading ? <Spinner /> : <Content />}
{items.length > 0 && <List />}
```

**Vue:**

```vue
<Spinner v-if="isLoading" />
<Content v-else />

<List v-if="items.length > 0" :items="items" />
```

### Loops

**React:**

```jsx
{products.map(p => <ProductCard key={p.id} product={p} />)}
```

**Vue:**

```vue
<ProductCard
    v-for="product in products"
    :key="product.id"
    :product="product"
/>
```

### Props Passing (`:` prefix = dynamic binding)

**React:**

```jsx
<ProductCard product={product} isHighlighted={true} count={5} />
```

**Vue:**

```vue
<!-- Static string -->
<ProductCard title="Hello" />

<!-- Dynamic (: prefix binds a JS expression) -->
<ProductCard :product="product" :is-highlighted="true" :count="5" />
```

### Slots (replaces React children/slots)

**React:**

```jsx
<Card>
    <p>Content</p>
</Card>
```

**Vue:**

```vue
<!-- In Card.vue -->
<template>
    <div class="card">
        <slot /> <!-- default slot = children -->
    </div>
</template>

<!-- Usage -->
<Card>
    <p>Content</p>
</Card>
```

Named slots:

```vue
<!-- Layout.vue -->
<template>
    <div>
        <header><slot name="header" /></header>
        <main><slot /></main>
    </div>
</template>

<!-- Page.vue -->
<template>
    <Layout>
        <template #header>
            <h1>Page Title</h1>
        </template>
        <p>Body content</p>
    </Layout>
</template>
```

